        <P>Check in, explore, find your friends and win at the 2011 CES!&nbsp; Follow the International CES on Foursquare at <A href="http://foursquare.com/intlces" target=_blank>http://foursquare.com/intlces</A>&nbsp; for tips and tricks to get around this year’s show. Check in at&nbsp;five of the 10 official CES venues between Tuesday, January 4 and Sunday, January 9 to earn the official, coveted 2011 CES Foursquare badge.<BR><BR>Once you earn your official 2011 CES Foursquare badge, stop by the Experience CEA booth in Central Hall to get your official 2011 CES Foursquare button (the first 2,000). <BR><BR><A href="/docs/FoursquareAtCESOfficialRules.pdf" target=_blank>Read the official rules.<BR></A><BR><STRONG>2011 CES Check-In Locations </STRONG></P>
